I was signing up to audition for American Idol. I think I have a really good shot. My only fear is that they say you can't have talent representation, and I do.

56
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:17,000
In fairness, Daryl did tell me that joke, so I feel like I can say it.

57
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,000
Daryl's funny.

58
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,000
I know, right?

59
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,000
Hey, Andy?

60
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,000
Yeah?

61
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,000
Can I talk to you a second about these client memos?

62
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,000
Sure.

63
