What's going on?

64
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,000
Are you still in love with Erin?

65
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,000
What?

66
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:46,000
Because I am. I need to get her back. I can't be alone anymore. Andy, do you like being alone with me right now?

67
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,000
No, this is horrifying.

68
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:55,000
No, I don't like being alone with me either. Okay? I have to get Erin back. Are you still going to date her?

69
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,000
We're just friends, okay?

70
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,000
Do you promise that?

71
